Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can more-or-less tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to take a guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.78,sign_8205_123_Hmm_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,1)}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.74,Default,Brown,0000,0000,0000,,Sasahara, Sakamoto-sensei's calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.10,Default,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,And it was just getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.39,Default,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come back to this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So it {\i1}is{\i0} Sasahara-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd be interested in stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're after Senpai, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not any of your business, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want her to reject you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You started ignoring me\Never since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Because people supposedly tease you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:26.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do {\i1}you{\i0} like it when people think\Nwe're weirdly attached and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like it when people\Nthink we're close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want people\Nspreading rumors about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing that for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.45,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, for {\i1}my{\i0} sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You just suddenly started ignoring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So did you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:47.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who hated me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares either way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We both hate each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go to the same\Nschool as you if I hated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga, you idiot, can you\N{\i}still{\i0} not figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a problem\Ntalking to anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,and yet you ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You were indifferent\Nto everyone else, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought you'd never\Nbe interested in anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:17.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why Sasahara-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All right, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking about how you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You've been worried for me\Nall this time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Because, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,...we've been friends for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We've been friends for a long time? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.27,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think I'd do all this for you\Njust because we've been friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you just said you don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}absolutely{\i0} hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,S-So you {\i1}do{\i0} hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:54.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So, what? You joined the astronomy\Nclub just to piss me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.14,Default,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.00,Default,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's Kaga-kun's crush—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.58,Default,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.76,sign_6908_96_The_End,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:13.47,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed to my crush,\Nand now we're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.52,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But things have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.46,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,...a bit awkward since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,G-Goda-kun, let's walk home together—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kamine,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have club work. Maybe some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:32.74,sign_12175_187_Watching_You_Fro,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)}Watching You From Afar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.65,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Maybe we should have stayed friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.53,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nah, we've only just started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.66,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be more proactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kamine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I had stuff to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made you wait, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here late on days I have club work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, why don't we—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not safe to go home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.45,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I have you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Only until my bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.77,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he didn't want to go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.25,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm just \Nmaking him uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.99,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, Goda-kun's just a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.69,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:19.14,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did he avoid me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.72,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.37,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's worried he might\Nbe sweaty from club work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.56,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.90,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.04,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't avoiding me, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kamine, let's stop doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I should have told you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time dating anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what it's supposed to be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:48.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been thinking, and this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to make this easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.22,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I probably shouldn't\Ntell you like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for going out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.80,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.00,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, I didn't mean to make you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go back to how things were?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe not exactly how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we try\Nholding hands or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a relationship, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, was it too early?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, weren't you about to dump me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dump you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I never said anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:42.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I just meant we should stop\Nbeing so tense around each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:46.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Was I the only one who was getting tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:47.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I had the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:51.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I, well, thought it would be weird\Nto start acting like a boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as we started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:57.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So I was trying to act like everything\Nwas how it had always been,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but that's kind of cold, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been thinking\Nabout your walk home and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Was that uncalled-for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:12.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you avoid me\Nwhen I tried to get next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was sweaty from club work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, it's because I'm shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.40,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.78,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Such{\i1} an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.80,Flashback,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.01,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was Nanase...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.76,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:53.15,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, can you take these apples\Nto Nanase-san's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} go, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.39,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get in a fight with Kaoru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:06.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't, but she kind of hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.56,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Kaoru-chan had a crush on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:13.17,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, was this still a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.85,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, forget I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:29.76,Default,Derps,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: We Don't Need Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.92,Next_Ep,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}We Don't Need Girls
